  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Conquest map</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated and randomized battles in conquest map are changing the aspects of every battle. Featuring many different battle types, armies and skill of their commander, different biomes and many unique glyphs that affect both fighting sides equally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/024ed1b6877e8e288652b75afe6dc344.poster.avif?t=1764964319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/024ed1b6877e8e288652b75afe6dc344.webm?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/024ed1b6877e8e288652b75afe6dc344.mp4?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Your Army</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin battle with few production buildings and grow into an unstoppable force. Production buildings are continuously creating new units, forming the composition of your army. What you decide to build will determine strengths and weaknesses of your army.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/91d2548eaab67c23c46d3d877f7dc903.poster.avif?t=1764964319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/91d2548eaab67c23c46d3d877f7dc903.webm?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/91d2548eaab67c23c46d3d877f7dc903.mp4?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Units</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are different types of armor and damage. Countering your opponent's armor is the key to the victory. Every unit has its own unique look and ability. The majority of abilities are useful most of the time and some abilities are more specialized that give you more ways to outplay your opponent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/0b5c4d6439d8548e16c37d50fffa42d1.poster.avif?t=1764964319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/0b5c4d6439d8548e16c37d50fffa42d1.webm?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/0b5c4d6439d8548e16c37d50fffa42d1.mp4?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create your own deck</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each match you will be rewarded with a new deck ability. You can mix rare abilities from other factions. But there is a limit of how many rare, epic and legendary abilities you can place into your deck. There are more than a hundred unique deck abilities that you can collect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/ae246b9a2aaf6f11ec747503c8a0de1a.poster.avif?t=1764964319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/ae246b9a2aaf6f11ec747503c8a0de1a.webm?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/ae246b9a2aaf6f11ec747503c8a0de1a.mp4?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story campaign</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You start your journey as a knight sent by his royal decree to inspect local villages. What should have been a routine task however turns into a darker turn. Ancient evil is rising in the shadows and soon it will be revealed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/d6ea6ce9aafb008899ffc1afa7707beb.poster.avif?t=1764964319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/d6ea6ce9aafb008899ffc1afa7707beb.webm?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/d6ea6ce9aafb008899ffc1afa7707beb.mp4?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Conquest map</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated and randomized battles in conquest map are changing the aspects of every battle. Featuring many different battle types, armies and skill of their commander, different biomes and many unique glyphs that affect both fighting sides equally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/024ed1b6877e8e288652b75afe6dc344.poster.avif?t=1764964319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/024ed1b6877e8e288652b75afe6dc344.webm?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/024ed1b6877e8e288652b75afe6dc344.mp4?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build Your Army</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin battle with few production buildings and grow into an unstoppable force. Production buildings are continuously creating new units, forming the composition of your army. What you decide to build will determine strengths and weaknesses of your army.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/91d2548eaab67c23c46d3d877f7dc903.poster.avif?t=1764964319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/91d2548eaab67c23c46d3d877f7dc903.webm?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/91d2548eaab67c23c46d3d877f7dc903.mp4?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Units</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are different types of armor and damage. Countering your opponent's armor is the key to the victory. Every unit has its own unique look and ability. The majority of abilities are useful most of the time and some abilities are more specialized that give you more ways to outplay your opponent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/0b5c4d6439d8548e16c37d50fffa42d1.poster.avif?t=1764964319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/0b5c4d6439d8548e16c37d50fffa42d1.webm?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/0b5c4d6439d8548e16c37d50fffa42d1.mp4?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create your own deck</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each match you will be rewarded with a new deck ability. You can mix rare abilities from other factions. But there is a limit of how many rare, epic and legendary abilities you can place into your deck. There are more than a hundred unique deck abilities that you can collect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/ae246b9a2aaf6f11ec747503c8a0de1a.poster.avif?t=1764964319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/ae246b9a2aaf6f11ec747503c8a0de1a.webm?t=1764964319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3636000/extras/ae246b9a2aaf6